des:
Toscana Dynamic can be paired with your smart assistant to control your Toscana pergola with intutive voice commands. It allows you to control the coverings, curtains, lights, and much more.

Every Toscana Pergola product include Dynamic System, you need a Toscana Dynamc enabled pergola to use this skill

You can simply ask Alexa to control your Toscana Pergola. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our Toscana Dynamic app in app market then register an account;
(2). Configure our devices in our Toscana Dynamic app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4). Search Toscana Dynamic skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5). Enable Toscana Dynamic skill, and you'll be navigated to Toscana Dynamic app login page;
(6). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7). Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the pergola light.”
“Alexa, turn off the pergola light.”
“Alexa, set the pergola light to 50%.”
“Alexa, open the cover.”
“Alexa, close the cover.”
